 demoDrawBoxes(form posn size rows cols);sf;boxsize;starts;n;sizes;radii;fstyles;fcol;fills
⍝ Draw a subform and put boxes in it

 sf←form,'.BX'
 sf eWC'SubForm' ('Posn' posn)('Size' size)
 boxsize←size÷rows cols
 n←≢starts←⌊,(¯.95++⍳rows cols)×⊂boxsize
 sizes←n⍴⊂⌊0.9×boxsize
 radii←5 5 ⍝ n⍴⊂5 5
 fcol←n⍴⊂0 0 0 ⍝ Black
 fills←n⍴↓ 255×⍉2 2 2⊤¯1+⍳16
 fstyles←n⍴0 ¯1
 (sf,'.R1') eWC'Rect' (↓⍉↑starts) (↓⍉↑sizes) (radii) fcol ('FillCol' fills)('FStyle' fstyles)
